OL,3,CHolocaust survivor's memorial bench
OL,4,Cdestroyed in 'act of hatred'
OL,6,FA memorial bench dedicated to a
OL,7,FHolocaust survivor who found safety in
OL,8,Fthe UK has been destroyed in "an
OL,9,Fapparent act of antisemitic hatred".
OL,11,FParts of the bench were found dumped
OL,12,Fin a frozen lake in Clowes Park in
OL,13,FSalford on Wednesday 8 January, having
OL,14,Fbeen ripped from the ground and
OL,15,Fsmashed into pieces.
OL,17,FThe bench was dedicated to Chaim
OL,18,FFerster, who survived eight
OL,19,Fconcentration camps during the Second
OL,20,FWorld War before moving to Salford.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
