OL,6,F"We expect those responsible to be
OL,7,Fidentified and prosecuted to the
OL,8,Ffullest extent of the law."
OL,10,FA spokesperson for Greater Manchester
OL,11,FPolice confirmed they are
OL,12,Finvestigating the destruction.
OL,14,FThey said: "We are aware of a
OL,15,FHolocaust memorial bench being damaged
OL,16,Fand found in the lake in Clowes Park,
OL,17,FSalford yesterday. It's currently
OL,18,Funknown who the offenders are and we
OL,19,Fare currently investigating.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
