OL,6,F"We take these kinds of incidents
OL,7,Fextremely seriously and are following
OL,8,Fall lines of enquiry."
OL,10,FThe North West Friends of Israel also
OL,11,Fcondemned the vandalism.
OL,13,FThey said: "Chaim Ferster educated
OL,14,Fthose on his past because he feared
OL,15,Fthe Holocaust would be forgotten in
OL,16,Fgenerations time. The audio bench
OL,17,Fpreserved his wartime experiences,
OL,18,Fallowing members of the public to
OL,19,Flisten to parts of his stories.
