OL,6,FIn his late 70s he began speaking
OL,7,Fabout his experiences and dedicated
OL,8,Fmuch of the remainder of his life to
OL,9,Fspeaking to schoolchildren about the
OL,10,FHolocaust.
OL,12,FThe bench was unveiled in 2019 on the
OL,13,Froute of his daily walk.
